le=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Residual Heat Indicator</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Indicates that the glass is hot and therefore, one should be careful when touching it and when placing items on it as they might be damaged.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Timer with Automatic Stop</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Turns off the active zone once the set time elapses.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Booster Function</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Allows you to focus all the power of the induction cooktop (hob) in the preset zone, to speed up the boiling and cooking times.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Slide Controls</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">This handy \\u201ctouch control\\u201d system makes it possible, for example, to increase or decrease the operating temperature by sliding your finger from right to left or vice versa.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Child Safety</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Once this function has been set and until it is disabled, the induction cooktop (hob) does not turn on by turning on the controls.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Overheating and Liquid Spill Protection</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">If the cooktop (hob) overheats or liquid spills occur, a safety device trips and stops operation.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Limited 2 Year Parts and Labor Warranty</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>California Proposition 65</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">WARNING: Cancer and Reproductive Harm</p><p><a href=\\\"http://www.P65Warnings.ca.gov\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">www.P65Warnings.ca.gov</a></p></div>.<br><br><strong>Freight Charges May Apply</strong><br><br></div>      </div>      <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_accessories\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab\\\" aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_accessories\\\" data-slug=\\\"accessories\\\" role=\\\"tab\\\" aria-selected=\\\"false\\\" tabindex=\\\"-1\\\"> <span class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtext\\\">Accessories</span> </span></h3>      <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_accessories\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_accessories\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\">         <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\">            <div class=\\\"woocommerce-Tabs-panel woocommerce-Tabs-panel--accessory panel entry-content wc-tab\\\" id=\\\"tab-accessory\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"tab-title-accessory\\\">\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"product_accessory_container\\\">                            <div class=\\\"product_accessory_box\\\">                                <a href=\\\"/products/ilve-a48401/\\\">                                <div class=\\\"product_accessory_image\\\">                                    <img loading=\\\"lazy\\\" width=\\\"115\\\" src=\\\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/marketplace-midmanphilippines/us.ilve.com/refs/heads/main/wp-content/uploads/A48401_p20025.jpg\\\">                                </div>                                <div class=\\\"product_accessory_title\\\">ILVE A/484/01 11 inch Chopping Board</div>                                <span class=\\\"woocommerce-Price-amount amount\\\"><bdi><span class=\\\"woocommerce-Price-currencySymbol\\\">$</span>252.00</bdi></span>                                </a>                            </div>                            <div class=\\\"product_accessory_box\\\">                                <a href=\\\"/products/ilve-uagq36ss/\\